   Ezoic Terms of Use

   Ezoic Inc, a Nevada corporation (“Ezoic”) provides the website located
   at www.ezoic.com (“ezoic.com”), all the content under this domain,
   certain related software, and it’s services to you subject to the
   following terms and conditions. By using Ezoic you agree to be bound be
   the latest amended versions of this Agreement and Ezoic’s Privacy and
   Security Policy (see “Modifications” below).

   SECTION 1: ACCEPTING THE TERMS

   Ezoic optimizes, caches, alters, monetizes, collects data, and serves
   your website to end users. Services include but are not limited to
   analytics tools, reporting and optimization tools and services. By
   using the information, tools, features and functionality located on
   Ezoic.com, through any Ezoic APIs, or through any software or other
   websites that interface with Ezoic.com or its APIs, (collectively the
   “Service”), you agree to be bound by this Agreement, whether you are a
   “Visitor” (meaning you merely browse the Ezoic.com website) or you are
   a “Member” (meaning you have registered with Ezoic). The term “you” or
   “User” refers to a Visitor or a Member. If you wish to become a Member
   and make use of the Service you must read this Agreement and indicate
   your acceptance during the Registration process. If you accept this
   Agreement, you represent that you have the capacity to be bound by it
   or, if you are acting on behalf of a company or entity, that you have
   the authority to bind such entity.

   SECTION 2: COPYRIGHTS

   All content included on Ezoic.com, such as text, graphics, logos,
   button icons, images, audio clips, digital downloads, data
   compilations, and software, as well as the compilation of that content
   into one, coherent website, is the property of Ezoic and protected by
   United States and international copyright laws. Reproduction of the
   content of Ezoic.com without the written permission of Ezoic is
   prohibited.

   SECTION 3: TRADEMARKS AND SERVICEMARKS

   Ezoic, the Ezoic logo, and other Ezoic graphics, logos, page headers,
   button icons, scripts, and service names are trademarks, certification
   marks, service marks, or other trade dress of Ezoic or its
   subsidiaries. Ezoic’s trademarks, certification marks, service marks,
   and trade dress have inherent meaning and substantial value because of
   their restricted use. They may not be used in connection with any
   product or service that is not Ezoic’s, in any manner without Ezoic’s
   permission. All other trademarks not owned by Ezoic or its subsidiaries
   that appear on Ezoic.com are the property of their respective owners,
   who may or may not be affiliated with, connected to, or sponsored by
   Ezoic or its subsidiaries.

   SECTION 4: LICENSE TO ACCESS EZOIC.COM AND SERVICES AND AVAILABILITY

   In consideration for accessing Ezoic.com and the Service, Ezoic grants
   you a limited license to access and make personal use of the website.
   This license prohibits your downloading (other than page caching) or
   modifying any portion of it, except with express, written consent of
   Ezoic. This license does not allow resale of Ezoic’s services without
   Ezoic’s written permission. You may not frame or utilize framing
   techniques to enclose any trademark, logo, or other proprietary
   information (including images, text, page layout, or form) of Ezoic.com
   without express written consent of Ezoic. You may not use any meta tags
   or any other “hidden text” utilizing Ezoic’s name or trademarks without
   the express written consent of Ezoic. Any unauthorized use
   automatically terminates the permission or license granted by Ezoic and
   may incur legal liabilities for any damages. You are granted a limited,
   revocable, and nonexclusive right to create a hyperlink to any
   non-password protected directories. You may not use any of Ezoic’s
   proprietary graphics or trademarks as part of the link without express
   written permission.

   EZOIC MAKES NO GUARANTEE REGARDING THE LEVEL OF PAGEVIEWS OR AD
   IMPRESSIONS OR CLICKS OR THE AMOUNT OF PAYMENT MADE TO YOU UNDER THIS
   AGREEMENT. IN ADDITION, FOR THE AVOIDANCE OF DOUBT, EZOIC DOES NOT
   GUARANTEE THE SERVICE WILL BE AVAILABLE AT ALL TIMES OR DURING ANY DOWN
   TIME (i) CAUSED BY OUTAGES TO ANY PUBLIC INTERNET BACKBONES (ii) CAUSED
   BY ANY FAILURES OF YOUR EQUIPMENT, SYSTEMS OR SERVICES, (iii) FOR
   PREVIOUSLY SCHEDULED MAINTENANCE (iv) CAUSED BY A TECHNICAL ERROR,
   CODING ERROR, UPDATES, MAINTENANCE AND REPAIR (v) RELATING TO EVENTS
   BEYOND EZOIC’S CONTROL SUCH AS STRIKES, RIOTS, INSURRECTION, FIRES,
   FLOODS, EXPLOSIONS, WAR, GOVERNMENTAL ACTION, LABOR CONDITIONS,
   EARTHQUAKES, NATURAL DISASTERS OR INTERUPTIONS TO INTERNET SERVICES IN
   AN AREA WHERE EZOIC OR YOUR SERVERS ARE LOCATED OR CO-LOCATED. EZOIC
   RESERVES THE RIGHT TO SUSPEND OR INTERRUPT ACCESS TO THE SERVICE OR
   PORTIONS OF OUR WEBSITE, AT ANY TIME, WITH OR WITHOUT NOTICE.

   LIMITATIONS ON REVERSE ENGINEERING, DECOMPILATION, AND DISASSEMBLY.

   You may not reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble the Service or
   any software made available to you through ezoic.com, ezoic.net or it’s
   related services, except and only to the extent that such activity is
