   SECTION 5: ACCOUNTS AND PASSWORDS

   YOU MAY ONLY HAVE ONE EZOIC ACCOUNT. If you are issued an account, you
   are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and
   password, and you agree to accept responsibility for all activities
   that occur under your account or password. Ezoic reserves the right to,
