Popular Ezoic Platform Features

   

Ad Tester

   Ad Tester allows websites to perform automated ad placement testing.
   Ezoic learns how visitors respond to ad density, placements, and
   various networks. Then, automatically makes adjustments to maximize
   earnings and balance visitor experiences
   Ad Tester Info
   

Layout Tester

   Ezoic’s Layout Tester allows publishers to test multiple website
   layouts (mobile, desktop, or tablet) and then automatically adjusts the
   site to deliver each visitor the layout that is going to best balance
   user experience and revenue.
   Layout Tester Info
   

Header Bidding

   Ezoic simplifies the setup of a server-side competitive bidding auction
   for your ad inventory live on your site. Existing bidding partners can
   compete with Ezoic partners over ad inventory. Ezoic makes setting up
   and managing header bidding easy.
   Header Bidding Info
   

Big Data Analytics

   Ezoic’s Big Data Analytics allows publishers to track visitor
   engagement and authentic behavior on their digital properties. This
   gives publishers access to data — unavailable through Google Analytics
   — around SEO, ad earnings, & more.
   Big Data Analytics Info
   

AMP Converter

   Ezoic’s AMP Converter creates AMP versions of your site’s pages without
   the typical loss in functionality or earning potential. Ezoic is a
   certified Google Partner and includes all of Ezoic’s existing
   multivariate testing technology inside of AMP.
   AMP Converter Info
   

Site Speed Tools

   Ezoic helps automate some of the most difficult parts of speeding up a
   website. Ezoic provides a free CDN, advanced caching intelligence, and
   a site speed app designed to implement Google’s best practices
   automatically without any complications.
   Site Speed Info

